->What about 1 day delivery?
:1 day delivery is a demanding addon option. Add 1 day delivery if emergency while ordering with addon for the service. It adds some fees since your task will be prioritized over others and shorter time period.

->Which Linux Operating Systems are applicable?
:Almost all linux operating systems.

->What about post or after delivery support?
:I try to give support as much as possible after delivery of successful operation. But it is limited to 1 week after delivery.

->What if the service is ordered without discussion and confirmation?
:The order will be canceled via support or you will have to pay more reasonable fees regarding the service.

->Do you provide Monthly Maintenance Service?
:Yes. Please Contact me for this.

->Which shared hosting companies are good for you?
:All type of shared , cloud and VPS hosting servers are good to work with.



